metadata.name: Primordial
metadata.description:
omnis amor oriundi

Intro:

I am a shadow of myself ... 
but from this dustiness ... 
all the richness will come.

Genesis:

This void is boring as FVCK ... 
Speaking to myself SVCKS ... 
Used my extra eye to see what is thought 
About the state of nothing and as objective observers with nothing to do 
I open my face hole 
In tongues, like my vision of the Tower of Babel 
In a chant, over and over 
"FVCK Shadows, the first ALPHA!"
